{"thi-ap24:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap24:0.2":"Kundalakesivagga ","thi-ap24:0.3":"Sakulatheriapadana ","thi-ap24:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","thi-ap24:1.2":"sabbadhammana paragu; ","thi-ap24:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","thi-ap24:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","thi-ap24:2.1":"Hitaya sabbasattanam, ","thi-ap24:2.2":"sukhaya vadatam varo; ","thi-ap24:2.3":"Atthaya purisajanno, ","thi-ap24:2.4":"patipanno sadevake. ","thi-ap24:3.1":"Yasaggapatto sirima, ","thi-ap24:3.2":"kittivannagato jino; ","thi-ap24:3.3":"Pujito sabbalokassa, ","thi-ap24:3.4":"disasabbasu vissuto. ","thi-ap24:4.1":"Uttinnavicikiccho so, ","thi-ap24:4.2":"vitivattakathankatho; ","thi-ap24:4.3":"Sampunnamanasankappo, ","thi-ap24:4.4":"patto sambodhimuttamam. ","thi-ap24:5.1":"Anuppannassa maggassa, ","thi-ap24:5.2":"uppadeta naruttamo; ","thi-ap24:5.3":"Anakkhatanca akkhasi, ","thi-ap24:5.4":"asanjatanca sanjani. ","thi-ap24:6.1":"Maggannu ca maggavidu, ","thi-ap24:6.2":"maggakkhayi narasabho; ","thi-ap24:6.3":"Maggassa kusalo sattha, ","thi-ap24:6.4":"sarathinam varuttamo. ","thi-ap24:7.1":"Mahakaruniko sattha, ","thi-ap24:7.2":"dhammam desesi nayako; ","thi-ap24:7.3":"Nimugge kamapankamhi, ","thi-ap24:7.4":"samuddharati panine. ","thi-ap24:8.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","thi-ap24:8.2":"jata khattiyanandana; ","thi-ap24:8.3":"Surupa sadhana capi, ","thi-ap24:8.4":"dayita ca sirimati. ","thi-ap24:9.1":"Anandassa maharanno, ","thi-ap24:9.2":"dhita paramasobhana; ","thi-ap24:9.3":"Vemata bhagini capi, ","thi-ap24:9.4":"padumuttaranamino. ","thi-ap24:10.1":"Rajakannahi sahita, ","thi-ap24:10.2":"sabbabharanabhusita; ","thi-ap24:10.3":"Upagamma mahaviram, ","thi-ap24:10.4":"assosim dhammadesanam. ","thi-ap24:11.1":"Tada hi so lokagaru, ","thi-ap24:11.2":"bhikkhunim dibbacakkhukam; ","thi-ap24:11.3":"Kittayam parisamajjhe, ","thi-ap24:11.4":"aggatthane thapesi tam. ","thi-ap24:12.1":"Sunitva tamaham hattha, ","thi-ap24:12.2":"danam datvana satthuno; ","thi-ap24:12.3":"Pujitvana ca sambuddham, ","thi-ap24:12.4":"dibbacakkhum apatthayim. ","thi-ap24:13.1":"Tato avoca mam sattha, ","thi-ap24:13.2":"‘nande lacchasi patthitam; ","thi-ap24:13.3":"Padipadhammadananam, ","thi-ap24:13.4":"phalametam sunicchitam. ","thi-ap24:14.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap24:14.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","thi-ap24:14.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","thi-ap24:14.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","thi-ap24:15.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayada, ","thi-ap24:15.2":"orasa dhammanimmita; ","thi-ap24:15.3":"Sakula nama namena, ","thi-ap24:15.4":"hessati satthu savika’. ","thi-ap24:16.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap24:16.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap24:16.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap24:16.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap24:17.1":"Imamhi bhaddake kappe, ","thi-ap24:17.2":"brahmabandhu mahayaso; ","thi-ap24:17.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","thi-ap24:17.4":"uppajji vadatam varo. ","thi-ap24:18.1":"Paribbajakini asim, ","thi-ap24:18.2":"tadaham ekacarini; ","thi-ap24:18.3":"Bhikkhaya vicaritvana, ","thi-ap24:18.4":"alabhim telamattakam. ","thi-ap24:19.1":"Tena dipam padipetva, ","thi-ap24:19.2":"upatthim sabbasamvarim; ","thi-ap24:19.3":"Cetiyam dvipadaggassa, ","thi-ap24:19.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","thi-ap24:20.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap24:20.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap24:20.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap24:20.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap24:21.1":"Yattha yatthupapajjami, ","thi-ap24:21.2":"tassa kammassa vahasa; ","thi-ap24:21.3":"Pajjalanti mahadipa, ","thi-ap24:21.4":"tattha tattha gataya me. ","thi-ap24:22.1":"Tirokuttam tiroselam, ","thi-ap24:22.2":"samatiggayha pabbatam; ","thi-ap24:22.3":"Passamaham yadicchami, ","thi-ap24:22.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap24:23.1":"Visuddhanayana homi, ","thi-ap24:23.2":"yasasa ca jalamaham; ","thi-ap24:23.3":"Saddhapannavati ceva, ","thi-ap24:23.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap24:24.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","thi-ap24:24.2":"jata vippakule aham; ","thi-ap24:24.3":"Pahutadhanadhannamhi, ","thi-ap24:24.4":"mudite rajapujite. ","thi-ap24:25.1":"Aham sabbangasampanna, ","thi-ap24:25.2":"sabbabharanabhusita; ","thi-ap24:25.3":"Purappavese sugatam, ","thi-ap24:25.4":"vatapane thita aham. ","thi-ap24:26.1":"Disva jalantam yasasa, ","thi-ap24:26.2":"devamanussasakkatam; ","thi-ap24:26.3":"Anubyanjanasampannam, ","thi-ap24:26.4":"lakkhanehi vibhusitam. ","thi-ap24:27.1":"Udaggacitta sumana, ","thi-ap24:27.2":"pabbajjam samarocayim; ","thi-ap24:27.3":"Na cireneva kalena, ","thi-ap24:27.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","thi-ap24:28.1":"Iddhisu ca vasi homi, ","thi-ap24:28.2":"dibbaya sotadhatuya; ","thi-ap24:28.3":"Paracittani janami, ","thi-ap24:28.4":"satthusasanakarika. ","thi-ap24:29.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thi-ap24:29.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thi-ap24:29.3":"Khepetva asave sabbe, ","thi-ap24:29.4":"visuddhasim sunimmala. ","thi-ap24:30.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thi-ap24:30.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thi-ap24:30.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thi-ap24:30.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thi-ap24:31.1":"Yassatthaya pabbajita, ","thi-ap24:31.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thi-ap24:31.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thi-ap24:31.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo. ","thi-ap24:32.1":"Tato mahakaruniko, ","thi-ap24:32.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","thi-ap24:32.3":"Dibbacakkhukanam agga, ","thi-ap24:32.4":"sakulati naruttamo. ","thi-ap24:33.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap24:33.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap24:33.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap24:34.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap24:34.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap24:34.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap24:35.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap24:35.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap24:35.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap24:36.1":"Ittham sudam sakula bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap24:37.1":"Sakulatheriyapadanam catuttham. "}